WEBVTT

00:07.222 --> 00:09.061
<i>Previously, on</i>
"Ray Donovan"...

00:12.199 --> 00:13.293
Two...

00:13.381 --> 00:14.652
Three!

00:36.238 --> 00:38.660
‐ Oh, God!
‐

01:14.121 --> 01:15.675
Can you tell me
where you were

01:15.763 --> 01:17.535
on the night
of November 7th?

01:22.299 --> 01:23.902
My dad needs a favor.

01:23.996 --> 01:25.261
Fuck it!

01:33.507 --> 01:34.892
The fuck...

01:51.702 --> 01:53.175
May he rest in fuckin' peace.

01:53.378 --> 01:54.910
<i>Slainte.</i>

01:59.464 --> 02:00.918
Ray‐Ray.

02:04.872 --> 02:07.316
<font color=#FF00FF>*RAY DONOVAN*</font>
